### Create Index
PUT http://localhost:9200/payment_cards
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "settings": {
    "number_of_shards": 1,
    "number_of_replicas": 0
  },
  "mappings": {
    "properties": {
      "card_name": {"type": "text"},
      "card_type": {"type": "keyword"}
    }
  }
}

